1.55
log
@We are done providing support for the vax.
lots of agreement.
@
text
@define(MACHINE,vax)dnl
vers(__file__,
	{-$OpenBSD: MAKEDEV.md,v 1.54 2015/10/23 15:14:12 claudio Exp $-},
etc.MACHINE)dnl
